snippet.title: Crash Team Rumble™ - Gameplay Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Crash is back in an all-new 4v4 online multiplayer rumble. See all the action to come in Season 1! All seasonal Heroes, Maps, Powers and Limited Time Modes are available for free with the purchase of the game.

Pre-order #CrashTeamRumble today, and play with friends on June 20!

PRE-ORDER NOW: https://bit.ly/3Lovlut

Follow Crash!
